---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: "A cozy corner of the internet for 1980s-inspired book and movie reviews."
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="hero-title__neon">Neon</span>
    <span class="hero-title__rewind">Rewind</span>
    <span class="hero-title__reviews">Reviews</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-tagline">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
  <p class="hero-intro">
    Welcome to <strong>Neon Rewind Reviews</strong>, a cozy corner of the internet where we
    revisit books and movies through a totally 1980s&#8209;inspired lens. Grab your VHS tapes,
    mixtapes, and dog&#8209;eared paperbacks&mdash;let&rsquo;s hit rewind.
  </p>
  <a href="/reviews/" class="btn-primary">Browse All Reviews</a>
</section>

<section class="latest-reviews">
  <h2 class="section-heading">Latest Reviews</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    {% for review in collections.latestReviews %}
      {% include "partials/review-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
